# airom-rules signing public key (ed25519, base64 of the 32-byte key on one line).
#
# The private half lives only in the airom-rules repository's CI secret
# (AIROM_RULES_SIGNING_KEY) and signs each release bundle's manifest. Rotation:
# generate a new keypair, replace the line below, and ship an airom release.
syEx+bushIfWXkxoEV6dyEW+tWKG4eP9VXzp5H233HA=
